snippet.title: Feather - Nintendo Switch / PC Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy It Now!
Nintendo Switch eShop - https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/feather-switch
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/545040/Feather/
Discord - https://discord.gg/samuraipunk

Feather is a serene game about exploration and immersion in a beautiful landscape. Become a bird, fly around and lose yourself in zen-like flow whilst listening to the soothing ambient soundtrack.

Trailer Produced by Travers Dunkinson
